
Keys
help defaultkeys
Ctrl X like Ctrl k when no selection

Switch panes	Ctl W
prev/next tab	Alt ,/.
find next		Ctrl N


Options

diffgutter
paste and smartpaste
colorschemes
	set colorscheme darcula


Pipes

micro | cat - outputs to cat when buffer is closed
ifconfig | cat - sends output to micro


Regex capture groups are now supported in the replace command. Examples:
> replace "(foo)" "$1-bar"
> replace "(foo)" "${1}-bar"
> replace "(?P<group>foo)" "$group-bar"
> replace "(?P<group>foo)" "$group-bar"
> replace "(?P<key>\w+):\s+(?P<value>\w+)$" "$key=$value"

Recommended colourshemes
	monokai (also the default colorscheme)
	zenburn
	gruvbox
	darcula
	twilight
	railscast
	bubblegum (light theme)
	
